                    <note xml:lang="en" type="abstract" xml:id="abstract-en-809">
                        <quote source="#bib809-1">Bp. of Seleucia-Ctesiphon and Cath. When Yahbalaha was elected, the Christians in
            the Persian Empire enjoyed the freedom accorded to them by <persName>Emperor Yazdgard I</persName> and
